OL,6,FPerspectus' study suggests 53% of
OL,7,FBrits over the age of 40 believe
OL,8,Finsults were of a gentler nature back
OL,9,Fin the day, with 60% feeling they were
OL,10,Fmore jovial than modern day put downs.
OL,12,FA resounding 72% of all ages polled,
OL,13,Fagreed Brits have a unique style when
OL,14,Fit comes to slights, while 81% felt it
OL,15,Fwas a very British trait, to insult
OL,16,Fyour loved ones, as a back handed term
OL,17,Fof endearment.
